  @api @features_first
  Scenario: Test the Blog archive
    Given I visit "john"
      And I click "Blog"
      And I should see "Blog posts by month"
     When I visit "john/blog/archive/all"
      And I should see "First blog"
      And I visit "john/blog/archive/all/201301"
